        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "And when it was told me how that the Jews laid wait for the man",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] In the oldest MSS. there is no mention made of “the Jews.” The ",
        "children": []
