        "class": "ital",
        "text": "I sent straightway to thee",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] i.e. I sent him. The pronoun is supplied in the ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Rev. Ver.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " as needful to the sense. Of course Lysias implies by his language that he felt that Felix was a more fit person than himself to deal with such a case.",
